"""wsq - Slurm queue monitor with curses TUI and static output modes.

Usage:
    wsq                  # TUI mode, auto-refresh every 5s
    wsq --static         # One-shot print to stdout (aliased as 'sq')
    wsq -m               # Scope: my jobs only
    wsq -a               # Scope: all cluster jobs
    wsq -r               # Filter: running jobs only
    wsq -t               # Show ETAs for pending Priority jobs
    wsq -n 10            # Set TUI refresh interval (seconds)
"""
